<HEAD>People in the News</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto NY44</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Former President and Mrs. Reagan attended a
black-tie preview of composer Andrew Lloyd Webber's stage spectacle
``The Phantom of the Opera.''
   The sold-out performance Saturday night at the Music Center's
Ahmanson Theatre was a benefit for the center. The show's official
